Explosive_Drone.help: You creates two Seeker Drones. These Seeker Drones will follow you until they detect an enemy and then they will zero in on their targets and detonate on impact. The small explosive flash of energy does only minor damage, but the concussion can weaken foes. Affected targets will have reduced Damage, Accuracy and Perception and may even be Disoriented for a short while. You can only ever have Two Seeker Drones out at one time and they can be destroyed by your foes. Recharge: Long
Explosive_Drone.shortHelp: Summon Seekers: Ranged Disorient, -DMG, -ACC, -Perception, Low DMG(Energy)

Transition.help: The Arachnos Flier can accelerate to higher speeds while moving at non-combat speed.
